5%2FBVVGN7UPRYGFI47MNRWUUSRD4M%2F&h=5146b364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20171105/BVVGN7UPRYGFI47MNRWUUSRD4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n.........新井和我對很多東西和事物看法是一樣的，唯有三文魚不同，我是絕對不吃生的，但新井說一般的老百姓還是吃的，由日本人養殖，衞生上有保障，到百貨公司或鄉下壽司店，還擺在主要位子上，這也是在日本做家庭主婦養成的觀點吧。<br />\n<br />\n我不吃三文魚刺身，與新派和老派有關，與價錢無關，新派人吃，老派人不吃，我屬於老派。<br />\n(蔡瀾)"},{"pid":"ae49d36509699866720a8be7fd740277ce948c1d","tid":2238560,"uid":296589,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"日本三文魚壽司先係搶手貨<br />\n超市百搭壽司最少係配有係三文魚, 亦係最多人想要"},{"pid":"7c437bb1ddfd02050ba76e8f9c4582ddcdab3ca7","tid":2238560,"uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:43:43.000Z","msg":"日本人好尊重蔡欄唔食蔡欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd64b9fc54f4474885c074ba622ff4e3de75899","tid":2238560,"uid":78243,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:44:50.000Z","msg":"三文魚唔食日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948fc20630a1665351372593b8139a3f14d16bfe","tid":2238560,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:46:15.000Z","msg":"三文魚好唔尊重av女優<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302f3c818faa18957be1004d6eb8d474a9199c25","tid":2238560,"uid":370061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:48:21.000Z","msg":"av女優上嘅三文魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177794b7aa25988aecc279078fef25b439b862b6","tid":2238560,"uid":16567,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"日本人唔係唔食三文魚<br />\n<br />\n相反係好鍾意食<br />\n<br />\n但以前只會熟食唔食生食<br />\n<br />\n因為多寄生蟲<br />\n<br />\n而家日本做魚生三文魚全部係挪威進口<br />\n<br />\n所以生有三文魚刺生"},{"pid":"1475fbde4de01ec0b24c5c65e3810278e8f736cf","tid":2238560,"uid":11703,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:52:18.000Z","msg":"等我講番少少喇<br />\n日本人將三文魚用喺壽司上係由90年代開始<br />\n嗰時因為挪威嘅三文魚產量過剩<br />\n要搵方法外銷<br />\n之後搵上咗日本<br />\n初時不停摸門釘<br />\n嗰時日本人完全接受唔到呢種食法<br />\n<br />\n但挪威嗰邊冇放棄<br />\n不停推廣呢種食法<br />\n之後終於有成果<br />\n有壽司連鎖店（唔記得邊間，好似係スシロー)接納<br />\n之後就大賣<br />\n直到現在成為非常受歡迎嘅壽司<br />\n<br />\n利申：上年睇財經節目ガイアの夜明け講嘅"},{"pid":"193e2d118f62c1d24ace195c7b518eac2ed2cc8a","tid":2238560,"uid":109560,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be86e73c88bb842db4b93f76284ff4031f6ca20b","tid":2238560,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20171105/BVVGN7UPRYGFI47MNRWUUSRD4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20171105%2FBVVGN7UPRYGFI47MNRWUUSRD4M%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=0fc8a3bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20171105%2FBVVGN7UPRYGFI47MNRWUUSRD4M%2F&h=5146b364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20171105/BVVGN7UPRYGFI47MNRWUUSRD4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n.........新井和我對很多東西和事物看法是一樣的，唯有三文魚不同，我是絕對不吃生的，但新井說一般的老百姓還是吃的，由日本人養殖，衞生上有保障，到百貨公司或鄉下壽司店，還擺在主要位子上，這也是在日本做家庭主婦養成的觀點吧。<br />\n<br />\n我不吃三文魚刺身，與新派和老派有關，與價錢無關，新派人吃，老派人不吃，我屬於老派。<br />\n(蔡瀾)"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"係咪真係有新派老派，定係菜san自己分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e3bf1f9f346d23eefe1933cbc9485728cf7c41","tid":2238560,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"193e2d118f62c1d24ace195c7b518eac2ed2cc8a","tid":2238560,"uid":109560,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be86e73c88bb842db4b93f76284ff4031f6ca20b","tid":2238560,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/2